com.google.gwt.dev.shell
Class ModuleSpace

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.dev.shell.ModuleSpace
All Implemented Interfaces:
ShellJavaScriptHost
Direct Known Subclasses:
ModuleSpaceOOPHM
public abstract class ModuleSpace
extends java.lang.Object
implements ShellJavaScriptHost

The interface to the low-level browser, this class serves as a 'domain' for a module, loading all of its classes in a separate, isolated class loader. This allows us to run multiple modules, both in succession and simultaneously.
